data.description: This well-maintained bi-level home is nicely situated on a corner lot in the Sonoma East area.   The exterior was recently painted, with a total square footage is 2323.  Some of the amenities include two living areas, one downstairs and one upstairs, mountain views, a separate parking area for toys or guests and much more!  This home is conveniently located for outdoor recreation, golf, shopping, healthcare, universities and more!   Please call to schedule your showing today!
